[00:00.14] Aloft all hands, strike the top-masts and belay
[00:03.04] Yon angry setting sun and fierce-edged clouds
[00:06.48] Declare the typhoon's coming
[00:08.25] Before it sweeps your decks, throw overboard
[00:11.01] The dead and dying – ne'er heed their chains
[00:14.17] Hope, hope, fallacious hope!
[00:16.32] Where is thy market now?